&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As a Customer Service Representative, you will complete a four week training program to become an expert in Beyond&#39;s financial hardship programs. After you successfully complete training, you will be responsible for providing superior customer service and a positive experience to our clients. The Client Success Specialist role is a remote position.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
