&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate will be a results-driven, strategic thinker able to thrive in a dynamic, rapid-growth environment. Exceptional candidates will have best-in-class data skills including SQL, Excel, dataset manipulation, data visualization, and presentation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
