&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Define and continually challenge KPIs critical to achieving company goals; lead the design of stakeholder dashboards and executive reporting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
